@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lbsmwv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((v0 + 0.20 / v0 + 0.92)))
    v1 = wp.exp(0.28)
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.14) / (v1 + 0.13 - tmp + 0.16)) * ((v2 + 0.90 + v0 + 0.11) / (tmp + 0.84 + v2 + 0.74)))
    v2 = wp.cos((0.68 + (v0 + 0.54 * v1 + 0.16)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.83 / tmp + 0.69) + (tmp + 0.63 * v1 + 0.95)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.05)) - (wp.sin(v0 + 0.93) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.64)))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
